{"ne3:0.1":"Netti ","ne3:0.2":"3. Niddesavara ","ne3:1.1":"Tattha sankhepato netti kittita. ","ne3:2.0":"3.1. Harasankhepa ","ne3:2.1":"Assadadinavata, ","ne3:2.2":"Nissaranampi ca phalam upayo ca; ","ne3:2.3":"Anatti ca bhagavato, ","ne3:2.4":"Yoginam <b>desanaharo</b>. ","ne3:3.1":"Yam pucchitanca vissajjitanca, ","ne3:3.2":"Suttassa ya ca anugiti; ","ne3:3.3":"Suttassa yo pavicayo, ","ne3:3.4":"Haro <b>vicayo</b>ti niddittho. ","ne3:4.1":"Sabbesam haranam, ","ne3:4.2":"Ya bhumi yo ca gocaro tesam; ","ne3:4.3":"Yuttayuttaparikkha, ","ne3:4.4":"Haro <b>yutti</b>ti niddittho. ","ne3:5.1":"Dhammam deseti jino, ","ne3:5.2":"Tassa ca dhammassa yam padatthanam; ","ne3:5.3":"Iti yava sabbadhamma, ","ne3:5.4":"Eso haro <b>padatthano</b>. ","ne3:6.1":"Vuttamhi ekadhamme, ","ne3:6.2":"Ye dhamma ekalakkhana keci; ","ne3:6.3":"Vutta bhavanti sabbe, ","ne3:6.4":"So haro <b>lakkhano</b> nama. ","ne3:7.1":"Neruttamadhippayo, ","ne3:7.2":"Byanjanamatha desananidananca; ","ne3:7.3":"Pubbaparanusandhi, ","ne3:7.4":"Eso haro <b>catubyuho</b>. ","ne3:8.1":"Ekamhi padatthane, ","ne3:8.2":"Pariyesati sesakam padatthanam; ","ne3:8.3":"Avattati patipakkhe, ","ne3:8.4":"<b>Avatto</b> nama so haro. ","ne3:9.1":"Dhammanca padatthanam, ","ne3:9.2":"Bhuminca vibhajjate ayam haro; ","ne3:9.3":"Sadharane asadha- ","ne3:9.4":"Rane ca neyyo <b>vibhatti</b>ti. ","ne3:10.1":"Kusalakusale dhamme, ","ne3:10.2":"Nidditthe bhavite pahine ca; ","ne3:10.3":"Parivattati patipakkhe, ","ne3:10.4":"Haro <b>parivattano</b> nama. ","ne3:11.1":"Vevacanani bahuni tu, ","ne3:11.2":"Sutte vuttani ekadhammassa; ","ne3:11.3":"Yo janati suttavidu, ","ne3:11.4":"<b>Vevacano</b> nama so haro. ","ne3:12.1":"Ekam bhagava dhammam, ","ne3:12.2":"Pannattihi vividhahi deseti; ","ne3:12.3":"So akaro neyyo, ","ne3:12.4":"<b>Pannatti</b> nama haroti. ","ne3:13.1":"Yo ca paticcuppado, ","ne3:13.2":"Indriyakhandha ca dhatu ayatana; ","ne3:13.3":"Etehi otarati yo, ","ne3:13.4":"<b>Otarano</b> nama so haro. ","ne3:14.1":"Vissajjitamhi panhe, ","ne3:14.2":"Gathayam pucchita yamarabbha; ","ne3:14.3":"Suddhasuddhaparikkha, ","ne3:14.4":"Haro so <b>sodhano</b> nama. ","ne3:15.1":"Ekattataya dhamma, ","ne3:15.2":"Yepi ca vemattataya niddittha; ","ne3:15.3":"Te na vikappayitabba, ","ne3:15.4":"Eso haro <b>adhitthano</b>. ","ne3:16.1":"Ye dhamma yam dhammam, ","ne3:16.2":"Janayantippaccaya paramparato; ","ne3:16.3":"Hetumavakaddhayitva, ","ne3:16.4":"Eso haro <b>parikkharo</b>. ","ne3:17.1":"Ye dhamma yammula, ","ne3:17.2":"Ye cekattha pakasita munina; ","ne3:17.3":"Te samaropayitabba, ","ne3:17.4":"Esa <b>samaropano</b> haro. ","ne3:18.0":"3.2. Nayasankhepa ","ne3:18.1":"Tanhanca avijjampi ca, ","ne3:18.2":"Samathena vipassanaya yo neti; ","ne3:18.3":"Saccehi yojayitva, ","ne3:18.4":"Ayam nayo <b>nandiyavatto</b>. ","ne3:19.1":"Yo akusale samulehi, ","ne3:19.2":"Neti kusale ca kusalamulehi; ","ne3:19.3":"Bhutam tatham avitatham, ","ne3:19.4":"<b>Tipukkhalam</b> tam nayam ahu. ","ne3:20.1":"Yo neti vipallasehi, ","ne3:20.2":"Kilese indriyehi saddhamme; ","ne3:20.3":"Etam nayam nayavidu, ","ne3:20.4":"<b>Sihavikkilitam</b> ahu. ","ne3:21.1":"Veyyakaranesu hi ye, ","ne3:21.2":"Kusalakusala tahim tahim vutta; ","ne3:21.3":"Manasa volokayate, ","ne3:21.4":"Tam khu <b>disalocanam</b> ahu. ","ne3:22.1":"Oloketva disalocanena, ","ne3:22.2":"Ukkhipiya yam samaneti; ","ne3:22.3":"Sabbe kusalakusale, ","ne3:22.4":"Ayam nayo <b>ankuso</b> nama. ","ne3:23.1":"Solasa hara pathamam, ","ne3:23.2":"Disalocanato disa viloketva; ","ne3:23.3":"Sankhipiya ankusena hi, ","ne3:23.4":"Nayehi tihi niddise suttam. ","ne3:24.0":"3.3. Dvadasapada ","ne3:24.1":"Akkharam padam byanjanam, ","ne3:24.2":"nirutti tatheva niddeso; ","ne3:24.3":"Akarachatthavacanam, ","ne3:24.4":"ettava byanjanam sabbam. ","ne3:25.1":"Sankasana pakasana, ","ne3:25.2":"Vivarana vibhajanuttanikammapannatti; ","ne3:25.3":"Etehi chahi padehi, ","ne3:25.4":"Attho kammanca niddittham. ","ne3:26.1":"Tini ca naya anuna, ","ne3:26.2":"Atthassa ca chappadani ganitani; ","ne3:26.3":"Navahi padehi bhagavato, ","ne3:26.4":"Vacanassattho samayutto. ","ne3:27.1":"Atthassa navappadani, ","ne3:27.2":"Byanjanapariyetthiya catubbisa; ","ne3:27.3":"Ubhayam sankalayitva, ","ne3:27.4":"Tettimsa ettika nettiti. ","ne3:27.5":"Niddesavaro. "}